description: Details of site construction method statement and management plan pursuant to condition 7 of planning permission ref: PP/2014/0681 dated 20/06/2014 for: construction of a single storey plant room building and an  external open plant and machinery compound (containing generators, fuel storage tanks, chillers and transformers) to the north of the main building, a single storey plant room building with a swan neck connection to the main building and an adjoining enclosed external open plant compound (containing generators, fuel storage tanks and transformers), to the west of the main building, alterations to the existing east plant building to include external cooling plant, new external lighting and fencing and temporary plant and machinery compounds to the north, east and west of the main building (following the removal of existing external plant and machinery).
